commit.title: Friendlier accumulator table for native compute w.r.t. naked pointers.
commit.message:
Friendlier accumulator table for native compute w.r.t. naked pointers.

Instead of unconditionally allocating the rel accu table at the process startup,
we delay its initialization until the first rel accu is generated. This way we
do not create naked pointers if the native compiler is never called.

(cherry picked from commit 9c69d189846336022a7d2c6f22691cccf503b3d3)

commit.message:
Friendlier accumulator table for native compute w.r.t. naked pointers.

Instead of unconditionally allocating the rel accu table at the process startup,
we delay its initialization until the first rel accu is generated. This way we
do not create naked pointers if the native compiler is never called.
